OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782829106
OL,3,CPrince William: Homelessness is a
OL,4,Csystemic issue
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales is expected to say
OL,7,Fthat homelessness is "not an
OL,8,Findividual failure; it is a systemic
OL,9,Ffailure" in a speech to mark the third
OL,10,Fanniversary of his initiative to show
OL,11,Fit's possible to end the issue.
OL,13,FPrince William launched Homewards in
OL,14,FJune 2023, in six locations across the
OL,15,FUK, in a bid to demonstrate it is
OL,16,Fpossible to make homelessness "rare,
OL,17,Fbrief and unrepeated".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782829106
OL,3,CPrince William: Homelessness is a
OL,4,Csystemic issue
OL,6,FAides say that the five-year programme
OL,7,Fis "seeing tangible results" and to
OL,8,Fdate has reached more than 2,400
OL,9,Fpeople through schools and the
OL,10,Fcommunity, supported over 250 people
OL,11,Finto employment, and helped more than
OL,12,F73 individuals and families, who may
OL,13,Fhave otherwise faced homelessness,
OL,14,Fmove into stable homes.
OL,16,FIt has invested #1.9 million across
OL,17,Fthe six locations through the
OL,18,FHomewards fund, with another #3.5
OL,19,Fmillion leveraged through grants and
OL,20,Fprivate philanthropy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782829106
OL,3,CPrince William: Homelessness is a
OL,4,Csystemic issue
OL,6,FIn a speech to mark the anniversary,
OL,7,FPrince William is expected to say:
OL,8,F"Homelessness is not an individual
OL,9,Ffailure; it is a systemic failure.
OL,10,FAnd, if systems help create the
OL,11,Fproblem, then systems can help prevent
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782829106
OL,3,CPrince William: Homelessness is a
OL,4,Csystemic issue
OL,6,F"By trialling new approaches,
OL,7,FHomewards is demonstrating how
OL,8,Fprevention can be embedded across
OL,9,Fevery part of our society. Proving
OL,10,Fthat our true strength emerges not in
OL,11,Fisolation, but in a shared purpose
OL,12,Fthat makes us greater than the sum of
OL,13,Four parts."
OL,15,FOver the last year, Homewards has
OL,16,Fmoved from testing ideas to putting
OL,17,Flarge-scale partnerships in place,
OL,18,Fincluding a #2.3 million furniture
OL,19,Fcollaboration with brands including
OL,20,FIKEA, B&Q and DfS to help people
OL,21,Festablish and sustain tenancies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782829106
OL,3,CPrince William: Homelessness is a
OL,4,Csystemic issue
OL,6,FThe Homelessness Data Lab has also
OL,7,Fbeen established, bringing together
OL,8,Fover 25 partners to explore how data
OL,9,Fand technology can help identify risk
OL,10,Fearlier.
OL,12,FWhen asked what her meetings with the
OL,13,FPrince were like, Hazel Detsiny,
OL,14,FExecutive Director of Homelessness at
OL,15,FThe Royal Foundation, replied:
OL,16,F"Punchy, I would say. But the question
OL,17,Fthat the Prince always asks me is 'How
OL,18,Fwill we know this has worked at the
OL,19,Fend of five years and how will we know
OL,20,Fit's worked for long-term change?'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782829106
OL,3,CPrince William: Homelessness is a
OL,4,Csystemic issue
OL,6,F"If we start to change the culture, if
OL,7,Fpeople across the whole society think
OL,8,Fdifferently, act differently, work
OL,9,Ftogether, feel optimistic, then that
OL,10,Fwill also be part of that sustainable
OL,11,Flong-term change that will spread to
OL,12,Fother places."
OL,14,FWilliam will be joined at an
OL,15,Fanniversary event on Wednesday by
OL,16,Fadvocates of the project, including
OL,17,FAston Villa footballer Tyrone Mings,
OL,18,FTV presenter Gail Porter, and Baroness
OL,19,FCasey.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782829106
OL,3,CPrince William: Homelessness is a
OL,4,Csystemic issue
OL,6,FLooking ahead, he will set out the
OL,7,Fnext phase of the project, saying:
OL,8,F"The next two years are about proving
OL,9,Fthat what works in six locations can
OL,10,Fwork across the country.
OL,12,FThe campaign is a major long-term
OL,13,Ffocus for William, who has spoken
OL,14,Fpreviously about how visiting shelters
OL,15,Fwith his late mother Diana, Princess
OL,16,Fof Wales, when he was a child, left a
OL,17,Fdeep and lasting impression and
OL,18,Finspired his work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
